WEBVTT

00:00:02.522 --> 00:00:06.851
Harry, wake up!
Come on, Harry, wake up!

00:00:16.702 --> 00:00:20.036
- Happy Christmas, Harry.
- Happy Christmas, Ron.

00:00:20.247 --> 00:00:22.453
What are you wearing?

00:00:23.041 --> 00:00:26.742
Oh, my mum made it.
Looks like you've got one too.

00:00:27.879 --> 00:00:30.287
- I've got presents?
- Yeah.

00:00:37.723 --> 00:00:39.798
There they are.

